Reasoning: The paper deals with sampling and reconstruction of signals, which falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT). The application of the method in wideband spectrum sensing of cognitive radio suggests that it may also fall under the sub-category of signal processing (cs.SP). The use of compressed sensing techniques and model order selection techniques suggests that it may also fall under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the use of sensor array imaging suggests that it may also fall under the sub-category of systems and control (cs.SI).
